N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 421.1 - Project applications

State Regulations

At the beginning of the annual project cycle, the
commissioner will announce the availability of applications for Conservation

Corps projects. The commissioner's announcement will include where to obtain
application information and the date by which applications must be
submitted. Notes
